    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. The S54 3.2L power plant remains in peak mechanical health, featuring a recently overhauled VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, ensuring the 333hp reaches the rear limited-slip differential without compromise. The suspension geometry is dialed in with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, providing the tactile feedback expected of a true driver\u2019s machine. No structural fatigue, zero fluid seepage, and a factory-original finish make this a definitive collector specimen.",
      "price": 46500.0,
