    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory-original paint retains its deep, glass-like luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip. The interior remains in showroom condition, featuring supple, untouched leather that still carries that distinct new-car aroma; there is absolutely no wear on the bolsters, buttons, or carpets. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using only OEM parts. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. Offered in turn-key condition for its next caretaker.",
