      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape\u2014it seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for something that's been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take a look. Can't wait to hear from you!",
