      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers short, tactile throws, mated to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the rear subframe mounting points inspected and verified. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-fresh compliance and rebound characteristics. Finished in a mirror-like coat with an interior devoid of bolster wear or UV damage, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
